把這種事稱為ＤＩＹ，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我還是覺得，就叫「做木工」比較搭啊。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要不要也做做看
