	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />我本來是這麼想的，<delay20 />
但你身上帶滿東西了吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等你騰出空位了，再跟我說啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
